questions.quote: You called everyone and said you were having trouble finding a Santa costume, so I borrowed one from a guy at work!
Hi, umm I know this is last minute, but we've decided to throw an impromptu baby shower for Rachel today.
Actually, I tried to call to you. You didn't need to come down here today.
Oh, hey, Mon, do you still have your like old blouses and dresses from high school?
Okay, listen, I'm thinking, why don't we just tell them who we really are? I mean, it'll be fine, I really think it'll be fine.
How could you pick up a hitchhiker?! He could be a rape-, a rapist or a killer or something!
Who do you think would win in a fight, Catwoman or Supergirl?
The reason we haven't told them we're together is because they hate me, okay? So will you fix this?
Does it matter? You're ultimately just gonna die or get divorced or have to blow your pets head off.
Really? Well, it seems to me if you'd done the right thing, I would not have woken up today feeling stupid and embarrassed, I would have woken up feeling comforted and satisfied!
